author: Kam Dhillon
title: Here’s Another Batch of Street Style From New York Fashion Week FW17
text:
Visit the original post to see all 24 images from this gallery. 
Location: New York, USA
Season: FW17
Key Looks: Those timeless adidas x Raf Simons kicks (slide #12), the man himself, Raf Simons, looking regal en route to Proenza Schouler’s FW17 show (slide #25), Vetements x Champion on show (slide #23), and the silver surfer donning the Arctic gray Palace puffer jacket from the brand’s FW16 drop (slide #20).
